{"id":215681,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/维权网-山东单县访民赵景华一家三代被关押在久/","date":"2012-03-16T07:39:49Z","modified":"2012-03-16T07:39:49Z","title":"维权网 | 山东单县访民赵景华一家三代被关押在久敬庄","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></span><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，因遭遇暴力拆迁而无家可归的山东单县访民赵景华偕老带幼，一家老少三代人到北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>下午，赵景华在宾馆休息，他的八旬老父母、妻子和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>岁的病儿到街上转转，竟被警察抓进府右街派出所，旋即被送往久敬庄关押。久敬庄关押访民，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>岁幼童到八旬老人皆不放过。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵景华一家老少三代人到北京上访，试图在二会期间向全国人大反映当地政府实施暴力拆迁，导致他一家三代人流离失所，并恳请人大调查处理当地政府的不法行为。赵景华没有见到人大代表，却得知妻儿父母反而被抓进久敬庄，不免忧心如焚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵景华呼吁媒体关注他一家老少三代人的悲惨遭遇，还他家人的人身自由，并依法保障他们上访的权利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵景华的手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15864659909</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1887160621140081693?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" heigh